  <section>
    <title>Installation and running</title>

    <para></para>

    <section>
      <title>Bluecove</title>

      <para>This will act as a bridge between you J2SE server apps running on
      the pc side and the Windows Bluetooth stack.</para>

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Download Bluecove at <ulink
          url="http://sourceforge.net/projects/bluecove/">http://sourceforge.net/projects/bluecove/</ulink></para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Unpack the
          <computeroutput>BlueCoveddmmyyyy.zip</computeroutput> in
          <computeroutput>$BLUECOVE_DIR</computeroutput>.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Put
          <computeroutput>$BLUECOVE_DIR/BlueCoveWinXP/intelbth.dll</computeroutput>
          in <computeroutput>c:/windows/system32</computeroutput></para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Create a directory for the example, we will call it
          <computeroutput>$BLUECOVE_EXAMPLE</computeroutput></para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Put
          <computeroutput>$BLUECOVE_DIR/BlueCoveWinXP/dist/lib/BlueCove-20050514.jar</computeroutput>
          in <computeroutput>$BLUECOVE_EXAMPLE</computeroutput></para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Benhui spp server example</title>

      <para>This is an example of a server in J2SE running on the pc
      side.</para>

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Dowload it at <ulink
          url="http://www.benhui.net/modules/Bluetooth/bluecove/net_benhui_bluecove_spp_examples_Nov_2004.zip">http://www.benhui.net/modules/Bluetooth/bluecove/net_benhui_bluecove_spp_examples_Nov_2004.zip</ulink></para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Unpack the file in
          <computeroutput>$BENHUI_BLUECOVE</computeroutput></para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Copy <computeroutput>$BENHUI_BLUECOVE/classes</computeroutput>
          in <computeroutput>$BLUECOVE_EXAMPLE</computeroutput></para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Run a command line : <programlisting>cd $BLUECOVE_EXAMPLE
java -classpath BlueCove-20050514.jar;classes net.benhui.bluecove.spp_console.SPP_Main</programlisting><figure>
