    <section>
      <title>Benhui BT gallery</title>

      <para>This contains a MIDLET application that will run on the mobile
      side as a client.</para>

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Download it at : <computeroutput><ulink
          url="http://www.benhui.net/modules/Bluetooth/codegallery/net_benhui_btgallery_oct2004.zip">http://www.benhui.net/modules/Bluetooth/codegallery/net_benhui_btgallery_oct2004.zip</ulink></computeroutput></para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Compile the MIDLET example (todo).</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Put the MIDLET in your mobile device using you're software
          provided with it (in my case Nokia PC Suite).</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Run the BtGalleryExample MIDLET from your mobile phone.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Select "Run Serial Client"</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Wait for device discovering</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Select the name of your pc running the server (option /
          select)</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Your mobile phone will ask you if you authorise the
          application to use the bluetooth connection : Answer yes</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Now your pc and your mobile device should have talked
          together</para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </section>
